{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":738,"text":"This is a vending machine in Los Angeles."},{"time":2746,"text":"It's in a shopping mall,\nand it sells fish eggs."},{"time":5887,"text":"It's a caviar-vending machine."}]},{"cues":[{"time":9837,"text":"This is the Art-o-mat,\nan art-vending machine"},{"time":11974,"text":"that sells small artistic creations\nby different artists,"},{"time":14708,"text":"usually on small wood blocks\nor matchboxes, in limited edition."}]},{"cues":[{"time":18423,"text":"This is Oliver Medvedik."},{"time":19616,"text":"He is not a vending machine,\nbut he is one of the founders of Genspace,"},{"time":23136,"text":"a community biolab in Brooklyn, New York,"},{"time":25127,"text":"where anybody can go and take classes"},{"time":26922,"text":"and learn how to do things\nlike grow E. coli that glows in the dark"},{"time":30100,"text":"or learn how to take strawberry DNA."},{"time":31876,"text":"In fact, I saw Oliver do\none of these strawberry DNA extractions"},{"time":34951,"text":"about a year ago, and this is what led me\ninto this bizarre path"},{"time":38012,"text":"that I'm going to talk to you right now."},{"time":39978,"text":"Strawberry DNA is really fascinating,\nbecause it's so beautiful."},{"time":43048,"text":"I'd never thought about DNA\nbeing a beautiful thing before,"},{"time":45856,"text":"before I saw it in this form."},{"time":47271,"text":"A lot of people, especially\nin the art community,"},{"time":49597,"text":"don't necessarily engage\nin science in this way."},{"time":51867,"text":"I instantly joined Genspace after this,"},{"time":53766,"text":"and asked Oliver, \"If we can do\nthis with strawberries,"},{"time":56374,"text":"can we do this with people?\""},{"time":57785,"text":"About 10 minutes later,\nwe were both spitting in vials,"},{"time":60438,"text":"coming up with a protocol\nfor human DNA extraction."},{"time":62980,"text":"I started doing this on my own."},{"time":64507,"text":"This is what my DNA actually looks like."}]},{"cues":[{"time":66493,"text":"And I was at a dinner party\nwith some artist friends,"},{"time":69068,"text":"and I was telling them about this project,"},{"time":71111,"text":"and they couldn't believe\nthat you could actually see DNA."},{"time":73853,"text":"So I said, all right, let's get out\nsome supplies right now."},{"time":76709,"text":"And I started having these bizarre\ndinner parties on Friday nights,"},{"time":79885,"text":"where people would come over\nand we'd do DNA extractions,"},{"time":82582,"text":"and I would capture them on video,"},{"time":84250,"text":"because it created\nthis kind of funny portrait as well."}]},{"cues":[{"time":86956,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":89469,"text":"These are people who don't necessarily\nregularly engage with science."},{"time":92894,"text":"You can kind of tell from their reactions."}]},{"cues":[{"time":95083,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":96906,"text":"But they became fascinated by it,"},{"time":98534,"text":"and it was really exciting for me\nto see them get excited about science."}]},{"cues":[{"time":101985,"text":"And so I started doing this regularly."}]},{"cues":[{"time":104139,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":105736,"text":"It's an odd thing to do\nwith your Friday nights,"},{"time":108039,"text":"but this is what I started doing."},{"time":109642,"text":"I started collecting a whole group\nof my friends' DNA in small vials"},{"time":112883,"text":"and categorizing them."},{"time":114084,"text":"This is what that looked like."},{"time":115553,"text":"And it started to make me think\nabout a couple of things."},{"time":118291,"text":"First, this looked a lot\nlike my Facebook wall."},{"time":120523,"text":"So in a way, I created\nsort of a genetic social network."}]},{"cues":[{"time":123735,"text":"And the second thing was,"},{"time":124994,"text":"one time a friend came over\nand looked at this on my table"},{"time":127807,"text":"and was like, \n\"Uh ... why are they numbered?"},{"time":130024,"text":"Is this person more rare\nthan the other one?\""},{"time":132325,"text":"And I hadn't even thought about that."},{"time":134135,"text":"They were just numbered"},{"time":135319,"text":"because that was the order\nthat I extracted the DNA in."},{"time":137954,"text":"But that made me think\nabout collecting toys,"},{"time":140088,"text":"and what's going on right now\nin the toy world with blind box toys,"},{"time":143327,"text":"and being able to collect these rare toys."},{"time":145410,"text":"You buy these boxes, but aren't sure\nwhat's going to be inside."},{"time":148431,"text":"But when you open them,\nyou have different rarities of the toys."},{"time":151462,"text":"I thought that was interesting;\nI thought about this"},{"time":153925,"text":"and the caviar vending machine\nand the Art-o-mat all together."},{"time":156858,"text":"And for some reason, I was one night\ndrawing a vending machine,"},{"time":159840,"text":"thinking of doing paintings\nof a vending machine."},{"time":162199,"text":"The vial of my DNA was sitting there,"},{"time":164003,"text":"and I saw a beautiful collaboration\nbetween the strands of DNA"},{"time":166953,"text":"and the coils of a vending machine."},{"time":168650,"text":"So I decided to create an art installation\ncalled the DNA Vending Machine."},{"time":172171,"text":"Here it is."}]},{"cues":[{"time":173429,"text":"(Music)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":178530,"text":"[DNA Vending Machine\nis an art installation"},{"time":180612,"text":"about our increasing access\nto biotechnology.]"}]},{"cues":[{"time":182838,"text":"(Music)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":187455,"text":"[For a reasonable cost,\nyou can purchase a sample of human DNA"},{"time":190437,"text":"from a traditional vending machine.]"}]},{"cues":[{"time":194719,"text":"(Music)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":213451,"text":"[Each sample comes packaged"},{"time":214789,"text":"with a collectible limited edition\nportrait of the human specimen.]"}]},{"cues":[{"time":218009,"text":"(Music)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":223370,"text":"[DNA Vending Machine treats DNA\nas a collectible material"},{"time":226127,"text":"and brings to light legal issues\nover the ownership of DNA.]"}]},{"cues":[{"time":228967,"text":"(Music ends)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":233313,"text":"Gabriel Barcia-Colombo:"},{"time":234488,"text":"The DNA Vending Machine is currently\nin a couple of galleries in New York,"},{"time":238025,"text":"and it's selling out pretty well."},{"time":239648,"text":"We're in the first edition of 100 pieces,"},{"time":241660,"text":"hoping to do another edition pretty soon."},{"time":243638,"text":"I'd like to get it\ninto more of a metro hub,"},{"time":245741,"text":"like Grand Central or Penn Station,"},{"time":247448,"text":"next to some of the other\nvending machines in that location."}]},{"cues":[{"time":250322,"text":"But really, with this\nand a lot of my art projects,"},{"time":252727,"text":"I want to ask the audience a question:"},{"time":254583,"text":"When biotechnology and DNA sequencing\nbecomes as cheap as, say, laser cutting"},{"time":258429,"text":"or 3D printing or buying caviar\nfrom a vending machine,"},{"time":262339,"text":"will you submit your sample of DNA\nto be part of the vending machine?"},{"time":265663,"text":"How much will these samples be worth?"},{"time":267474,"text":"Will you buy someone else's sample?"},{"time":269363,"text":"And what will you be able to do\nwith that sample?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":273096,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":274294,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}